Package xyz.kotlout.kotlout.model.experiment

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BinomialExperiment
    A specialization of the Experiment class for experiments involving binary outcomes.
    CountExperiment
    A specialization of the Experiment class for experiments involving integer counts.
    Experiment
    Base class for modelling experiments.
    HistogramComparator
    Allow two HistogramData objects to be compared so that an ArrayList of them can be sorted using Collections.sort()
    HistogramData
    Base class for data points which are needed to create histograms with the MPGraph library
    MeasurementExperiment
    A specialization of the Experiment class for experiments involving floating point measurements.
    NonNegativeExperiment
    A specialization of the Experiment class for experiments involving integers greater than or equal to zero.
    Post
    A Post is a class representing a question or reply posted to an experiment's discussion forum.
    StatCalculator
    Calculates the stats when an ArrayList of numbers is passed to its methods
